  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC434">
        <l>oḻiyicai yecca moḻiyicai muṭipiṉa.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/240/mode/1up">240</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/241/mode/1up">241</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, niṟutta muṟaiyāṉē oḻiyicaiyeccam uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : oḻiyicai yeccamāvaṉa mūṉṟu, avai, maṉṉai oḻiyicaiyum, tillai oḻiyicaiyum, ōkāra oḻiyicaiyum eṉa ; avai mūṉṟum, oḻiyicaip poruḷkoṇṭu muṭiyum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC434-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'kūriyatōr vāṇmaṉ'</l></lg>
<p>vāi kōṭiṟṟu, iṟṟatu eṉap piṉṉum vāḷmēlē muṭipu ceṉṟatu.</p>
<p>iṉi,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC434-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'varukatil koṇkaṉ'</l></lg>
<p>eṉa, varuka eṉappaṭṭāṉum avaṉē, koṇkaṉ eṉappaṭṭāṉum avaṉē ; ataṉāl, atuvum apporuḷkoṇṭu muṭintatu.</p>
<p>iṉik,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC434-Iḷam-cit3">
<l>'koḷalō koṇṭāṉ'</l></lg>
<p>eṉpuḻik, koḷalō eṉappaṭṭāṉaiyē koṇṭāṉ eṉpatu. ataṉāl, atuvum av voḻiyicaip poruḷkoṇṭu muṭintatu.	(38)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

